        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Ben2 is designed as a stateless microservice that processes due date requests via RESTful APIs. It supports both synchronous and asynchronous workflows, with built-in support for time zones and recurrence patterns. Key components include a scheduler engine, a rule evaluator, and a notification dispatcher, all optimized for low-latency responses in high-throughput environments."
