            "text": "Optimize Ben2 by tuning connection pools and caching frequently accessed due date data. Implement circuit breakers to handle downstream failures, and use exponential backoff for retries. Monitor latency metrics and adjust thread pools based on load. For error handling, log detailed traces with correlation IDs, and ensure fallback mechanisms, such as default due dates, to maintain system resilience during outages."
